{"tid":1033324,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[JYP員工入場踩] Somi確定5月初SOLO出道,Teddy擔任Producing","createTime":"2019-02-23T05:09:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T04:39:08.000Z","uid":74065,"like":18,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"257540d1556a3a3dd5abace10acc92a064dfa395","tid":1033324,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T05:09:53.000Z","msg":"23日上午，據歌謠界相關人士透露，Somi確定將於5月初作為SOLO歌手出道，目前她正以此為目標進行著最後的專輯製作。雖然現在還不確定是單曲還是迷你專輯的形式，但是不久前已經完成了錄音工作，正在計劃進行MV的拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，Somi通過個人ins賬號公開了在&quot;The Black Lable&quot;錄音室和工作人員一起拍的照片，而首張個人專輯將由Teddy擔任Producing。作為SOLO歌手的Somi將會展現什麼樣的音樂風格，和Teddy展現怎樣的化學反應受到粉絲矚目。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/h2QsS6Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fh2QsS6Y.jpg&h=c7d9689c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a656d07cd59f2684155c7acf5f350d78edd6b6","tid":1033324,"uid":63057,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T05:10:48.000Z","msg":"留名睇温屎踩somi"},{"pid":"e01b52dfd5b8b4fe63f99582bcb6839539f71af5","tid":1033324,"uid":223790,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T05:13:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab26f7a7a6148ac59cf12d21e07475eedfaa942a","tid":1033324,"uid":223790,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T05:13:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc090f28076108419606b0600b993598f22cc8dc","tid":1033324,"uid":223790,"like":7,"dislike":10,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T05:13:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7962b979e